data.description: You're looking at the ONLY 4 bed/3 full bath single story home ever offered for sale in the manned guard gated community of Summerchase within Point Aquarius! Quality construction by well-reputed, local Stylecraft home builder. Eye-catching brick & stone elevation w/ brick on all sides! Modern energy efficiency w/ double pane windows, Lennox AC system, 30-year dimensional shingle roof. Granite countertops, GE stainless appliances, walk-in pantry. Freshly painted interior w/ durable vinyl plank flooring throughout high traffic areas. Covered back patio w/ no rear neighbors! Auto garage door opener and irrigation system. TWO hot water heaters! Neighborhood amenities include boat launch, tennis & basketball courts, marina w/ boat slips, pool and playground.
